<h2 class="wprm-recipe-name wprm-block-text-bold">BBQ Chicken Dry Rub</h2>
<div class="wprm-spacer"></div>

<div class="wprm-spacer"></div>
<div class="wprm-recipe-summary wprm-block-text-normal"><span style="display: block;">This homemade bbq chicken rub adds sweet and smoky flavor to chicken. Use it as a dry brine or with your favorite bbq sauce. </span></div>
<div class="wprm-spacer"></div>
