								<h3 class="about-author-title">About Davinah &amp; Great Chicken Recipes</h3>
				<div class="about-author-content">
					<p>Hi! I'm Davinah, a wife, mom, foodie, recipe developer, and entrepreneur. I started Great Chicken Recipes as way to share some of my delicious and easy chicken recipes for busy people and families. Most are 30 minutes or less using wholesome and simple ingredients. </p>
				</div>
			</div>		<div id="block-19" class="mv_trellis_mobile_hide widget-container widget_block widget_text">
